00:26:02,111 --> 00:26:03,404
(cabinet drawer thuds)

538
00:26:03,738 --> 00:26:04,738
(cork squeaks)

539
00:26:04,906 --> 00:26:05,907
What a night.

540
00:26:11,454 --> 00:26:13,623
These girls are gonna
be the death of me yet.

