545
00:26:35,686 --> 00:26:36,938
Man, look at me.

546
00:26:41,526 --> 00:26:45,405
Yama Honda, memo: get the
girls a movie contract.

547
00:26:45,738 --> 00:26:48,783
(tense, eerie music)

548
00:26:56,791 --> 00:26:58,835
Hey, pal, what's your problem?

549
00:26:59,168 --> 00:27:00,795
